I want you to write a script using Kotlin Script language, script will be fow Windows   script should contain these actions:  

1)Create folders:
In script's directory create DoomRPG folder, it contains 2 folders - Game and Temporary
Temporary folder has 3 subfolders - Brew Binary, Desktop Binary and Files

2)Download necessary files:

Download these files

https://archive.org/download/doomrpg_brew/doomrpg.zip

https://github.com/Erick194/DoomRPG-RE/releases/latest

to Temporary/Files

Save paths to downloaded files

first one as brewBinary variable

second one as desktopBinary

3)Extract archives:
Extract brewBinary to Temporary/Brew Binary

Extract desktopBinary to Temporary/Desktop Binary

4)Final preparations
Copy folder Desktop Binary to script's root folder and rename it to Game

Copy file doomrpg.bar from folder Temporary/BREW Binary into Game folder

Run BarToZip.exe in Game folder

5)Run the game to check everything is okay


Run DoomRPG.exe